com.tlswe.awsmock.ec2.control

Class MockSecurityGroupController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tlswe.awsmock.ec2.control.MockSecurityGroupController

  • public final class MockSecurityGroupController
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory class providing static methods for managing life cycle of mock Security. The current implementations can:
    • create
    • delete
    • describe
    mock SecurityGroup.
